.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"04d2eb1f7cc1daa84b9696c5da89e9fd311fecba","tid":315700,"uid":117238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:02:14.000Z","msg":"作為一位細細個曾經寫過5P文兼比無數人屌過垃圾<br />\n到現在以寫正統小說為興趣既寫手<br />\n我有時候會唸<br />\n當初好多人都抵制所謂既5P文學 甚至到依家仲會拎番出黎恥笑一輪 因為係劇本口語文兼劇情清一色狗血垃圾<br />\n但望落去，真係唔覺得依家既講故台生態同5P文學到底相差有幾遠<br />\n覺得無奈"},{"pid":"c98af46ca41b63feb1603b5b379c0abd76544c6f","tid":315700,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T10:25:59.000Z","msg":"咁講真,成日話得愛情故,有人寫其他野你地係咪睇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見住自己既作品,一部反應差過一部,仲要係無人回覆既情況下但又有人比負評<br />\n真係心鳩淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095c234c2d5bfcf34c642f02e57401747edf5423","tid":315700,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:01:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啊 但佢地啲愛情故又唔係特別好睇<br />\n大部份正係識玩第一人稱 套路式嘅開頭<br />\n最重要係班人覺得易入手<br />\n以為自己正係識打字就得<br />\n我與其睇你寫甜<br />\n咁我不如睇翻阿里布達同秦守啲作品好過<br />\n高質過呢到個啲幾千倍</blockquote><br />\n讀者質素問題<br />\n我第一個出既故係用第一人稱加全口語,有200正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二個故用第三人稱加topic同對話係口語,其餘書面,得返40正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家果個第三人稱加全部書面語,結果負評就快多過正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者我應該真係接受連登只愛口語入文既風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好行太多生辟路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d56032a98df27e2dbbc284f0f417f1ac548cdf","tid":315700,"uid":117238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n我第一個出既故係用第一人稱加全口語,有200正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二個故用第三人稱加topic同對話係口語,其餘書面,得返40正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家果個第三人稱加全部書面語,結果負評就快多過正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者我應該真係接受連登只愛口語入文既風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好行太多生辟路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁真係要睇你寫文既初衷到底係咩<br />\n為左興趣？為左表達故事背後既意義？定只係為左討好連登既讀者，博下好評取暖？<br />\n講真，係市面上既文創作品佔主流既仍然係書面語文字，<br />\n只能問係咪真係值得？<br />\n至少我會堅持寫書面語"},{"pid":"0a26727ac5fc53b672998b42469f9d205d39f8bf","tid":315700,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:07:04.000Z","msg":"講故台大部份故都係垃圾<br />\n吹佢唔漲又有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好心班甜故on9仔打個丁清醒下"},{"pid":"aef09e8c0503e3f84651f34d9f26fde6767499c5","tid":315700,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我第一個出既故係用第一人稱加全口語,有200正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二個故用第三人稱加topic同對話係口語,其餘書面,得返40正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家果個第三人稱加全部書面語,結果負評就快多過正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者我應該真係接受連登只愛口語入文既風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好行太多生辟路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁真係要睇你寫文既初衷到底係咩<br />\n為左興趣？為左表達故事背後既意義？定只係為左討好連登既讀者，博下好評取暖？<br />\n講真，係市面上既文創作品佔主流既仍然係書面語文字，<br />\n只能問係咪真係值得？<br />\n至少我會堅持寫書面語</blockquote><br />\n我接受到無人睇,但無人睇之餘仲要埋黎伸一腳比個負評但唔出聲<br />\n就好似一個毒撚明明無人理,但拎高件衫望下個心口竟然無端端瘀晒咁<br />\n講真寫書面語同口語我覺得都有原因<br />\n我又唔係話完全寫死一種既,睇下點啦"}]}